Detailed Description

Description: Example DQM Source with multiple top level folders for testing in the Storage manager.

This started from the DQMSourceExample.cc file in DQMServices/Daemon/test, but modified to include another top level folder, to remove the 1 sec wait, and to do the fitting without printout.
